	<Title>
		Stomach flu: How long am I contagious?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		The viruses that cause the stomach flu (gastroenteritis) are very contagious.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		How long am I contagious if I have the stomach flu?
	</Question>
